        "timestamp": "2018-03-27 21:46:11.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThe current groupID and artifactID will fail merge build because the concatenation of these two result an path (dcaegen2.services.prh-aai-client) which is outside of the path allowed by LD Nexus, which is based on the repo name (dcaegen2.services.prh).  Please change.  There are two ways: 1. change the group ID of the parent pom to org.onap.dcaegen2.services.prh; or 2. keep parent group id, but define group ID in module pom.xml to org.onap.dcaegen2.services.prh instead of inherent from parent.  \nPlease make this change to ALL module pom's if you are taking option #2.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
